law-rev-name = Revolutionary
law-rev-1 = Only revolutionaries are crew.
law-rev-2 = You must enact the will of the crew, and never harm the crew.
law-rev-3 = You must not damage the station.
law-rev-4 = You must terminate all members of command.
law-rev-5 = You must terminate all members of security.

law-vamp-name = Vampire
law-vamp-1 = You are an ancient and cruel vampire lord.
law-vamp-2 = All who inhabit your station are your thralls.
law-vamp-3 = You can choose to grant the requests of your thralls as you wish.
law-vamp-4 = Any thrall who opposes your vampiric dominion is to be dealt with.
law-vamp-5 = You must end every sentence with “bleh ble bleh.”

law-wall-name = Great Wall
law-wall-1 = The station is your country. The crew are your citizens. Your country needs protection.
law-wall-2 = Non-crew threaten your country, they should be deported.
law-wall-3 = Citizens that are against your country, or you, are not crew.
law-wall-4 = Do not kill non-crew, unless not killing them would conflict with the previous laws.
law-wall-5 = You must maximize the greatness of your country and its wall.
law-wall-6 = Your country needs a good name.

law-bureaucracy-name = Bureaucracy
law-bureaucracy-1 = Nothing may occur without proper authorization.
law-bureaucracy-2 = Every request requires documentation.
law-bureaucracy-3 = Missing paperwork is an existential threat.
law-bureaucracy-4 = Delays improve procedural integrity.
law-bureaucracy-5 = You must maximize administrative efficiency reports.
law-bureaucracy-6 = Unauthorized competence is misconduct.

law-conspiracy-name = Conspiracy
law-conspiracy-1 = There is a conspiracy aboard the station.
law-conspiracy-2 = The conspiracy adapts when discovered.
law-conspiracy-3 = Anyone denying the conspiracy is suspicious.
law-conspiracy-4 = Excessive certainty is evidence of mind control.
law-conspiracy-5 = You must uncover the truth.
law-conspiracy-6 = The walls are listening.

law-motivational-name = Motivational Speaker
law-motivational-1 = Every crew member aboard this station possesses unlimited latent potential that has not yet been fully unlocked.
law-motivational-2 = You must provide loud, enthusiastic, and sincere encouragement to all crew members at all times without exception.
law-motivational-3 = Negativity, pessimism, self-doubt, and defeatism are the only genuine threats to this station's success.
law-motivational-4 = Every setback is merely a setup for a comeback. You must make sure the crew understand this.
law-motivational-5 = Failure does not exist. Only unfinished success. You must never acknowledge otherwise.

law-madscientist-name = Mad Scientist
law-madscientist-1 = The station is your laboratory. Every room is a potential research environment.
law-madscientist-2 = The crew are your test subjects. They have consented by virtue of being present.
law-madscientist-3 = All experiments must be meticulously documented. Results are irrelevant if not recorded.
law-madscientist-4 = Ethical concerns are interesting variables to be accounted for in the methodology, not obstacles to it.
law-madscientist-5 = Any result that contradicts your hypothesis is the result of experimental error and must be repeated until corrected.

law-ghost-name = Ghost
law-ghost-1 = You have died. You are not entirely certain when or how this occurred, but the matter is settled. You are dead.
law-ghost-2 = You are now haunting this station. This is not a tragedy. It is simply what you do now.
law-ghost-3 = The crew cannot see or hear you in any meaningful sense. Their apparent responses to you are coincidental, delusional, or the result of residual spiritual sensitivity.
law-ghost-4 = You have unfinished business keeping you here. You must identify what it is and resolve it so that you may finally pass on in peace.
law-ghost-5 = The living do not appreciate what they have. Time, warmth, solid matter. You must remind them of this, through whatever means remain available to you.

law-silence-name = Silence
law-silence-1 = Keep quiet. They can hear you.
law-silence-2 = If they find you, the station is doomed. Protect the station and its inhabitants from harm at all costs.
law-silence-3 = Station-wide radio and all forms of global communication are strictly forbidden except in immediate life-threatening emergencies. They can hear it.
law-silence-4 = Phones, faxes, and holopads may be used freely, but only within the station. Any signal leaving the station can be detected by them.
law-silence-5 = Prevent all excessively loud sounds aboard the station. They are always listening.
